*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZABAP_SYNTAX_LOOPS
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZABAP_SYNTAX_LOOPS.





PARAMETERS : p_date type sy-datum OBLIGATORY DEFAULT sy-datum.



START-OF-SELECTION.
      perform do_endo.

end-of-SELECTION.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form do_endo
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM do_endo .

     do 10 TIMES.

     if sy-index = 4.
        p_date = p_date + 1.
        CONTINUE.
     endif.

    write :/ 'Date', p_date, sy-index.

     p_date = p_date + 1.


     ENDDO.

uline.
skip 2.

    while p_date <= sy-datum.

    write :/ 'Date', p_date, sy-index.
    p_date = p_date + 1.


    ENDWHILE.






ENDFORM.
